{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"6026adb1-8910-43f7-a8df-63bb1fbddefb","content":"Use `dotnet watch test` with the `--filter` option:\n\n```bash\ndotnet watch test --filter \"FullyQualifiedName~ProcessPayment_NegativeAmount_ThrowsException\"\n```\n\nThis will:\n- **`dotnet watch test`** — re-run tests automatically on file save (hot reload)\n- **`--filter \"FullyQualifiedName~...\"`** — only run the matching test (`~` means \"contains\")\n\nYou can also filter by just the method name:\n\n```bash\ndotnet watch test --filter \"Name=ProcessPayment_NegativeAmount_ThrowsException\"\n```","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"c3828b1a-0f2e-4af3-bf0b-67a57fe54c1e","outputTokens":151,"requestId":"4C3D:1BD058:D0F481:10041F6:6A01340E"},"id":"43435fba-c60e-4f8e-a704-b9fc6847fb6a","timestamp":"2026-05-11T01:42:42.811Z","parentId":"a4383747-6481-44d6-a313-22668de1920a"}
